# PWA Icons

These icons should be generated for proper PWA support. Use a tool like:
- [PWABuilder Image Generator](https://www.pwabuilder.com/imageGenerator)
- [Favicon Generator](https://realfavicongenerator.net/)

Required sizes:
- 72x72 (minimum for PWA)
- 96x96
- 128x128
- 144x144
- 152x152
- 192x192 (with maskable support)
- 384x384
- 512x512

For the Google Docs disguise, use the Google Docs icon or create a subtle variation.

Maskable icons should have content in the "safe zone" (center 40% of the image).
